Scope
Company.

Level
Primary task.

Preconditions
Database contains the populations of: the world, continents, regions, countries, districts, and cities and the capital cities of each country.

Success End Condition
A report is available for the organisation to analyse.

Failed End Condition
No report is produced.

Primary Actor
Organisation

Trigger
A request for the data is made


